Package: CorMatCol
Type: Package
Title: Coloured Correlation Matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Slavenko
Maintainer: Alex Slavenko <gluttony14@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: cowplot,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    tibble,
    tidyr
Description: A single function to create a correlation matrix from a dataframe a list of variables.
    Optional arguments include an additional variable mapped to colour, pearson correlation coefficients,
    and some capabilities for visualization customization.
